data.description: Nestled within a quiet culdesac of Windstone Golf Course, this remarkable family home offers a blend of space for EVERYONE and EVERYTHING, comfort, and tranquility. Situated on a spacious lot at 9240 Shay Cove, this residence presents a rare opportunity to enjoy both elegant living and an active lifestyle in one of Ooltewah's most sought-after neighborhoods. Boasting expansive living space, this home provides ample room for large families, gatherings, and entertainment. With 4 large bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, there's no shortage of comfort and privacy for everyone. The back deck features a recently built gazebo that is perfect for outdoor dining.The two car garage has a ton of extra space for a workspace as well as two large vehicles. *Golf enthusiasts will appreciate the easy access to the renowned Windstone Golf Course. Enjoy world-class golfing just steps away from your front door.Community Amenities: As part of the Windstone community, residents have access to golf, clubhouse, tennis courts, pool & ponds.Located in Ooltewah, this home offers a serene suburban lifestyle while still being within reach of shopping, dining, schools, and major roadways for convenient commuting. Recent updates include Smart light switches throughout , All kitchen appliances are less than 4 years old, Upstairs unit is less than 4 years old,  Gazebo 2 years old, New smart  wireless garage door motor and Sunroom recently added
